column5: I hit the Bog today for a couple hours in the morning.  Fished about 4 fow on a sand bar, then the edge of a weedbed.  Both produced the same results, a whole lot of 5 inch perch, no eyes today.  maybe next week.
at least ya got out! good luck next time around...
Thanks fer the report, Steve. Will help on deciding the week-end plans.
I think this weekend I'm taking my little cousin to Island Lake on Saturday, then fishing Simcoe on Sunday.  should be fun.
